OL,5, Italian film director Lina Wertmuller, 
OL,6, the first woman ever to be nominated   
OL,7, for an Oscar for best director, has    
OL,8, died at the age of 93.                 
OL,10,FWertmuller passed away at her home in  
OL,11,FRome on Thursday morning, alongside    
OL,12,Ffamily and friends.                    
OL,14,FShe is credited with revolutionising   
OL,15,FItalian cinema in the 1970s and is     
OL,16,Fbest-known for her films Seven Beauties
OL,17,Fand the award-winning Swept Away.      
OL,19,FWertmuller received an honorary Oscar  
OL,20,Ffor lifetime achievement in 2019.      
